OL,7,FThe glaciers in the Pyrenees have
OL,8,Fbeen there for 100,000 years but they
OL,9,Fmay disappear within a lifetime, ITV
OL,10,FNews Science Correspondent Martin
OL,11,FStrew reports
OL,13,FWhen you picture Spain you think of
OL,14,Fsun, sea and perhaps sangria. But in
OL,15,Fthe Pyrenees mountain range, which
OL,16,Fruns along the border with France,
OL,17,Fthere is plenty of snow and rivers of
OL,18,Fslow moving ice, known as glaciers.
OL,19,FBut for how much longer?
